If you are looking for a safe way to  X2 your capital  this year
column2: you should definitely consider buying Ethereum in this price range.
there are two possible options of further price movements:

column1: Orange path   (~33%) : light touch of the support zone
column2: followed by a sharp pump upwards towards the $3200 resistance by the month of August 2025. Then some consolidation there and continuation with the coming of Autumn  (traditionally bullish season for crypto) .

column1: Red path   (~66%) : a full-fledged dive in the support zone
column2: down to $2150  (shadows can even reach $1950ish zone) . It will take more time
column3: but allow people to build more proper positions
column4: if they have not done so already. This dive can also help in gathering liquidity  (from liquidating early LONGs with high leverage
column5: everything with lev. higher than x6 will be washed down)  that will later be used for pushing the price  higher .

column3: but those who know Ethereum erratic behaviour they just... know. I will start accumulating  CRYPTOCAP:ETH  once it reaches $2450 and will continue doing it down to $2100 using x5 leverage  (if such price will ever be achieved) .
